From: Rafael J. Wysocki <rjw@sisk.pl>
Subject: non-contiguous pagedir for resume
Patch-mainline: no

This fixes problem where we could have enough memory on suspend, but
run out of contiguous memory on resume (and fail it).

Signed-off-by: Pavel Machek <pavel@suse.cz>

